ingredientsDesc:
Total β-hCG Specimen Diluent
1 Bottle (100mL) Total β-hCG Specimen Diluent in processed bovine and goat serum

二、IMx Total β-hCG MODE 1 Calibrator
MODE 1 CAL
1 Bottle (4mL) MODE 1 Calibrator. Concentration: 10mIU/mL hCG (human) in human serum.
6 Bottles (4mL each) of Total β-hCG Calibrators, A~F, concentration : 0, 10, 75, 250, 500 and 1000 mIU/mL
3 Bottles (8mL each) of Total β-hCG Controls, 25, 150 and 750 mIU/mL.

一、Reagent
1. 1 Bottle (6.5mL) Anti-β-hCG (Mouse, Monoclonal) Coaed Microparticles in TRIS buffer with protein stabilizers.
2. 1 Bottle (6.5mL) Anti-β-hCG (Goat, Polyclonal):Alkaline Phosphatase Conjugate in TRIS buffer with protein stabilizers.
3. 1 Bottle (10mL) 4-Methylumbelliferyl Phosphate, 1.2mM in AMP buffer.
4. 1 Bottle (20mL) Specimen Diluent in processed bovine and goat serum.
